---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PatternOfTheDay from "../components/PatternOfTheDay.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Home"
    description="The premier destination for Resume-Driven Development, Over-Engineering, and Resume-Padding. Why build simple solutions when you can build a distributed monolith?"
>
    <div class="intro">
        <h2>We make bad software.</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to the premier destination for Resume-Driven Development,
            Over-Engineering, and Resume-Padding. Why build simple solutions
            when you can build a distributed monolith managed by 4 different
            committees?
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bento-grid">
        <div class="potd-container">
            <PatternOfTheDay />
        </div>

        <div class="nav-cards">
            <a href="/patterns" class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3>Design Patterns</h3>
                    <span class="icon">üèóÔ∏è</span>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Discover the architectural patterns that ensure job
                    security. From "Distributed Monolith" to "Database as IPC",
                    these are the blueprints for eternal maintenance.
                </p>
                <div class="cta">Go to Hell &rarr;</div>
            </a>

            <a href="/radar" class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3>Tech Radar</h3>
                    <span class="icon">‚ò¢Ô∏è</span>
                </div>
                <p>
                    A curated list of technologies that should be illegal. We
                    track the industry's most successful cargo cults and zombie
                    frameworks.
                </p>
                <div class="cta">Get Radiated &rarr;</div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials">
        <h3>What "Experts" Say</h3>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <blockquote class="quote">
                "Thanks to Worst of Breed, we successfully migrated our 500-line
                PHP script to a Kubernetes cluster with 12 microservices.
                Latency increased by 4000%, but our resume value skyrocketed!"
                <cite>‚Äî Senior Enterprise Architect @ Fortune 500 Company</cite>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="quote">
                "Finally, a framework that understands that complexity IS the
                product. We now spend 90% of our time configuring YAML and 10%
                coding. Perfection."
                <cite>‚Äî Lead DevOps Ninja Rockstar</cite>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto">
        <h3>Our Manifesto</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>COMPLEXITY over Simplicity</li>
            <li>PROCESS over People</li>
            <li>TOOLS over Solutions</li>
            <li>RESUME over Value</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="signature">// We are Worst of Breed.</p>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .intro {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        border-bottom: var(--border-thick);
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        background: var(--ink);
        color: var(--paper);
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .card {
        background: var(--paper);
        border: var(--border-thick);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        transition:
            transform 0.2s,
            box-shadow 0.2s;
        text-decoration: none; /* override layout a style */
        height: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: translate(-5px, -5px);
        box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px var(--accent);
        background: var(--paper); /* override layout a:hover */
    }

    .card-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 2px dashed #ccc;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .card h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .cta {
        margin-top: auto;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: right;
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .bento-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .nav-cards {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .bento-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: stretch; /* Change start to stretch to match heights */
        }

        .potd-container {
            height: 100%;
            order: 2;
        }

        /* Make the POTD component fill height if possible, 
           though its content is dynamic */
        :global(pattern-of-the-day),
        :global(pattern-of-the-day .pattern-content),
        :global(pattern-of-the-day .brutalist-card) {
            height: 100%;
        }
    }

    .testimonials {
        margin: 4rem 0;
    }

    .testimonials h3 {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .testimonial-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .quote {
        border-left: 8px solid var(--accent);
        padding-left: 1rem;
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--paper);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .quote cite {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-style: normal;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--shadow);
    }

    .manifesto {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--ink);
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #f4f4f4;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .manifesto {
            margin-top: 5rem;
        }
    }

    .manifesto h3 {
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .manifesto ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .manifesto li::before {
        content: "[!] ";
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .signature {
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--shadow);
    }
</style>
